<slide title="The BLURB tag">
<blurb>
Used to display simple paragraphs optionally with a title in a larger font.  
The default value for each attribute is listed first.
</blurb>
<example><![CDATA[<blurb title="Blurb Title">

Paragraph of text.

</blurb>]]></example>

